# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __get__, __set__, __delete__ across all 14 asyncio subjects
#
# Covers the full matrix: 14 classes x 3 methods = 42 rows.
# __get__:    all false — no asyncio class is a descriptor.
# __set__:    all false — no asyncio class is a data descriptor.
# __delete__: all false — no asyncio class defines __delete__.
# asyncio provides event-loop concurrency primitives and I/O abstractions;
# none participate in Python's descriptor protocol.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

